    "content" : "Hi Folks .\n<br>I have been building this rare all white 21 window for a customer , have all but finished the metalwork now and its soon off to paint .\n<br>\n<br>Looks like it may be ready for Volksworld Show 2013 so you can get a look at all the work that has gone into this bus .\n<br>\n<br>The bus was dropped off at the workshop and I get to have a look for the first time in the flesh , Someone has repainted the bottom half in the States years ago but the M codes state its an original all white bus .\n<br>The belly pans are missing and the chassis is in a bad way.\n<br>\n<br>The unmistakable front end that we all wish to see as we open the garage door\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4746.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>Bus is very complete with all its samba bits - those removed are in good shape and the interior is in fantastic condition - This has already been removed - doors show some sign of rust\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4747.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>Back end looks straight - some bubbling on the tailgate \n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4748.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>Long panel shows some signs of rust at bottom\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4749.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>Cab floor will need some work - Drivers seat was still in - You get the idea with the condition of the interior\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4750.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>Sills show signs of rust as does the long panel where it meets the floor in the cargo area\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4751.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>Roof windows show signs of rust so will no doubt need some love\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4754.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>Cargo door shows signs of a previous repair - Black under seal painted at bottom\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4757.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>Floor also shows signs of repair - you may just see a screw head in the bottom right corner on the silver bulkhead\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4752.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>Window surrounds look ok on first look - we will see !!\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4768.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">",
