    "content" : "A look underneath revealed a bit of work required \n<br>\n<br>Main chassis rail\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4783.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>centre chassis cross member at back\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4782.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>rear outrigger\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4781.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>Next thing is to remove the floor to have a look at what its really like \n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4825.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>I get to see the repairs done in the past - New metal covered in black underseal then screwed together .\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4826.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>This was the section where the cargo doors shut\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4827.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>Floor out \n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4830.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>Top hat - bulkhead and the centre cross member at front are way beyond repair\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4831.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>The main chassis rail on the left side - The dark bits are holes \n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4833.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>Removed the remains of the belly pans from the rails \n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4841.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">",
