    "content" : "Cleaning the rail a bit to try to find the solid metal\n<br>You can also see the bracing I put in above the rails \n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4842.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>Just a few of the panels required for the bottom bits \n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4834.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>New chassis rails - All panels from Auto craft \n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4838.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>Lower section of chassis rail \n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4844.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>Main rail section\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4845.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>More holes below the top hat section\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4846.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>Replaced by new metal \n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4843.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>You can see repair below the top hat on the left\n<br>Also the bracing\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4849.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>The bit that curves up also needed repair - this has been done here and the rail cleaned up\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4850.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>Rail cleaned and ready for some protection\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4851.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">",
