    "content" : "A little more\n<br>Inner chassis is slightly porous \n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4856.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>Will need a section made up\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4855.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>New inner ready to go in\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4858.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>Long side sill shows all the signs of the same repairer \n<br>Black ****e - screws and multiple plates - This is rear jacking point\n<br>\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4859.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>This is the front jacking point on same side - Same repairs present\n<br>\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4860.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>Bottom of long panel opened up from outside\n<br>\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4861.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>Lower section removed from by the rear jacking point\n<br>\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4862.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>About 3/8 filler over the screws originally\n<br>\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4863.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>The lower section of the support posts\n<br>\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4864.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>The new centre chassis section fitted\n<br>\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4865.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">",
