    "content" : "A little more for you .\n<br>\n<br>Lining up the rear outrigger to make sure its straight \n<br>\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4866.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>Welded in place , again making sure its straight\n<br>\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4867.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>Top hat spot welded in place \n<br>\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4868.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>Welded to the chassis rail - to add extra strength.\n<br>\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4869.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>Back to the chassis rails - this is the offside at the front by the outrigger\n<br>\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4880.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>This is the rear outrigger on the offside \n<br>\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4881.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>A section of angle iron to add some strength whilst work is done on chassis\n<br>\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4882.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>A cross section of the front outrigger - showing previous repairs inside \n<br>\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4883.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>Out rigger roughly cut out \n<br>\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4884.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br>\n<br>Cleaned up a bit to find the solid metal\n<br>\n<br>\n<img src=\"http://i279.photobucket.com/albums/kk138/65-deluxe/Gareth%20Samba/IMG_4885.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">",
